Version 0.2.6
 * Translations updated
 * Tagged for Salix Live 13.1.1 release

Version 0.2.5
 * Added LXDE support
 * Added a warning message in case of missing swap partition
 * Added a warning message in case of no partitions at all

Version 0.2.4
